---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import AdSlot from '../../components/AdSlot.astro';
import ArticleSchema from '../../components/ArticleSchema.astro';
const datePublished = '2026-06-08';
const dateModified = '2026-06-11';
const today = new Date(datePublished).toLocaleDateString('id-ID', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' });
const bcItems = [{ label: 'Beranda', href: '/' }, { label: 'Blog', href: '/blog' }, { label: 'Cara Menentukan Harga Jual' }];
---
<Layout title="Cara Menentukan Harga Jual Produk UMKM 2026 — Strategi Profitable" description="Panduan menentukan harga jual produk UMKM: rumus cost-plus, value-based, competitor-based, dan psychological pricing. Plus 3 contoh kasus UMKM." keywords={['cara menentukan harga jual', 'harga jual produk umkm', 'cost plus pricing', 'value based pricing', 'strategi harga umkm']} canonical="https://hitungcerdas.net/blog/cara-menentukan-harga-jual" ogType="article">
  <ArticleSchema
    headline="Cara Menentukan Harga Jual Produk UMKM 2026 — Strategi Profitable"
    description="Panduan menentukan harga jual produk UMKM: rumus cost-plus, value-based, competitor-based, dan psychological pricing. Plus 3 contoh kasus UMKM."
    datePublished={datePublished}
    dateModified={dateModified}
    slug="cara-menentukan-harga-jual"
    articleSection="UMKM"
    keywords={['cara menentukan harga jual', 'harga jual produk umkm', 'cost plus pricing', 'value based pricing', 'strategi harga umkm']}
    wordCount={500}
  />

  <section class="article-hero" style="--cat-color:#EC4899;--cat-color2:#9D174D">
    <div class="wrap"><Breadcrumb items={bcItems} /><div class="article-tag">UMKM</div>
      <h1>Cara Menentukan Harga Jual Produk UMKM 2026 — Strategi Profitable</h1>
      <div class="article-meta"><span><i class="ti ti-calendar"></i> {today}</span><span><i class="ti ti-clock"></i> 7 menit baca</span><span><i class="ti ti-user"></i> Tim HitungCerdas</span></div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <AdSlot format="horizontal" />
  <article class="content-section"><div class="wrap-text">
    <p class="lead">Salah satu kesalahan terbesar UMKM Indonesia: harga jual asal-asalan tanpa hitung biaya tersembunyi. Banyak yang merasa untung, padahal saat dihitung detail malah <strong>rugi</strong>. Artikel ini bedah 4 strategi menentukan harga jual yang menguntungkan + 3 contoh kasus.</p>
    <h2>1. Strategi 1: Cost-Plus Pricing (Paling Common)</h2>
    <div class="formula-box"><p><strong>Harga Jual = HPP + (HPP × Markup %)</strong></p></div>
    <p>HPP = Bahan Baku + Biaya Produksi + Overhead. Markup typical: 30-100% tergantung industri.</p>
    <p>Contoh: HPP donut Rp 3.000, markup 100% → harga jual Rp 6.000.</p>
    <h2>2. Strategi 2: Value-Based Pricing</h2>
    <p>Harga berdasarkan <strong>nilai yang dirasakan pelanggan</strong>, bukan cost. Contoh: kopi specialty di cafe premium dijual Rp 50rb (HPP Rp 8rb), karena value experience.</p>
    <p>Cocok untuk: brand premium, produk unik, jasa konsultan.</p>
    <h2>3. Strategi 3: Competitor-Based Pricing</h2>
    <p>Cek harga kompetitor, lalu posisikan: lebih murah 5-10% (penetration), sama (parity), atau lebih mahal 10-20% (premium).</p>
    <h2>4. Strategi 4: Psychological Pricing</h2>
    <ul class="info-list"><li><strong>Charm pricing</strong>: Rp 99.999 terasa jauh lebih murah dari Rp 100.000</li><li><strong>Anchor pricing</strong>: tampilkan harga "coret" Rp 200rb, harga jual Rp 150rb</li><li><strong>Bundling</strong>: 3 item Rp 100rb (per item Rp 33rb feel lebih murah)</li><li><strong>Tier pricing</strong>: 3 paket (basic, standard, premium) — kebanyakan pilih tengah</li></ul>
    <AdSlot format="horizontal" />
    <h2>5. Contoh Kasus Real</h2>
    <h3>Kasus A: Baju Online</h3><p>HPP Rp 50rb (beli supplier). Biaya iklan IG Rp 10rb/order. Packaging Rp 5rb. Markup target 80%. Harga jual = (50 + 10 + 5) × 1.8 = <strong>Rp 117.000</strong> → rounded ke Rp 119.000 (charm).</p>
    <h3>Kasus B: Catering Box</h3><p>HPP Rp 18rb, target margin kotor 60%. Harga jual = 18 / (1 - 0.6) = <strong>Rp 45.000</strong>. Cek competitor sekitar Rp 40-50rb, sesuai.</p>
    <h3>Kasus C: Jasa Foto Wedding</h3><p>Cost Rp 2 juta per event. Pakai value-based: brand premium, foto cinematic, target market upper-middle. Harga: <strong>Rp 8-12 juta</strong>.</p>
    <h2>6. Tips Final</h2>
    <ul class="info-list"><li><strong>Hitung ALL cost</strong>: bahan, labor, packaging, ongkir, biaya iklan, listrik</li><li><strong>Sisakan margin untuk diskon</strong>: kalau pricing terlalu thin, gak bisa promo</li><li><strong>Test pricing</strong>: A/B test harga via promo terbatas, monitor response</li><li><strong>Naikkan harga bertahap</strong>: 5-10% per 6 bulan kalau positioning premium</li></ul>
    <div class="cta-box"><h3>🧮 Coba Kalkulator Harga Jual HitungCerdas</h3><p>Hitung harga jual optimal dengan auto-calc biaya tersembunyi.</p><p style="margin-top:14px"><a href="/kalkulator/harga-jual" class="btn btn-pri"><i class="ti ti-calculator"></i> Buka Kalkulator Harga Jual</a></p></div>
    <h2>Kesimpulan</h2><p>Harga jual yang tepat = balance antara profit + value pelanggan + posisi kompetitor. Jangan asal markup, hitung detail semua biaya.</p>
    <h3>📚 Artikel Terkait</h3><ul class="info-list"><li><a href="/blog/cara-menghitung-margin">Cara Hitung Margin Profit UMKM</a></li><li><a href="/kalkulator/invoice-generator">Invoice Generator</a></li><li><a href="/kalkulator/nama-bisnis-generator">Nama Bisnis Generator</a></li></ul>
  </div></article>
  <AdSlot format="horizontal" />
</Layout>
<style>
  .article-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cat-color) 0%, var(--cat-color2) 100%); color: #fff; padding: 20px 0 48px; }
  .article-hero :global(.breadcrumb-item), .article-hero :global(.breadcrumb-item a) { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .7); }
  .article-hero :global(.breadcrumb-item a:hover) { color: var(--gold-soft); }
  .article-hero :global(.breadcrumb-item span) { color: #fff; }
  .article-hero :global(.breadcrumb-item i) { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .4); }
  .article-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold-soft); letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 16px 0 12px; }
  .article-hero h1 { color: #fff; font-size: clamp(26px, 3.8vw, 42px); margin: 0 0 20px; max-width: 900px; line-height: 1.2; }
  .article-meta { display: flex; gap: 20px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .75); font-size: 13px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .article-meta span { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
  .lead { font-size: 17px !important; line-height: 1.7 !important; color: var(--text) !important; padding: 20px 24px; background: var(--bg-soft); border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid var(--cat-color); margin-bottom: 24px !important; }
</style>
